  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/e6d09c4b4d150f71a6c4d933d4fb07f2.poster.avif?t=1773782579\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/e6d09c4b4d150f71a6c4d933d4fb07f2.webm?t=1773782579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/e6d09c4b4d150f71a6c4d933d4fb07f2.mp4?t=1773782579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dispel is an adventure set in a dark fantasy world.<br><br>You are broke and decide to set off on a journey in search of wealth and fame. After dozens of cold nights in the forest, your eye catches an inconspicuous cave. Without hesitation, you rush straight into the very depth of it...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/d5aa27ec0d6abc440032790d1c179f18.poster.avif?t=1773782579\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/d5aa27ec0d6abc440032790d1c179f18.webm?t=1773782579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/d5aa27ec0d6abc440032790d1c179f18.mp4?t=1773782579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Procedural generation of levels. With procedurally generated levels, no two runs are ever the same, allowing for countless hours of gameplay.<br></li><li>Decide on how you want to play. Choose a unique class, race, and then continue to customize your character's appearance.<br></li><li>Play by exploring and combining any skill tree of your choice.<br></li><li>Challenge a unique setup of random curses that weaken your character. Find magic books containing powerful enchantments that help dispel the darkness.<br></li><li>Explore unique areas, each holds a variety of dangers, such as creepy monsters, exclusive bosses, and unrivaled traps.<br></li><li>Collect a full set of armor or combine different types. Create the strongest character ever.<br></li><li>Find all the secret levels to explore extensive locations with cities never seen before.<br></li><li>Non-target action combat</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/4d296e24b004850589d137c98c18c181.poster.avif?t=1773782579\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/4d296e24b004850589d137c98c18c181.webm?t=1773782579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/4d296e24b004850589d137c98c18c181.mp4?t=1773782579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/e6d09c4b4d150f71a6c4d933d4fb07f2.poster.avif?t=1773782579\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/e6d09c4b4d150f71a6c4d933d4fb07f2.webm?t=1773782579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/e6d09c4b4d150f71a6c4d933d4fb07f2.mp4?t=1773782579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dispel is an adventure set in a dark fantasy world.<br><br>You are broke and decide to set off on a journey in search of wealth and fame. After dozens of cold nights in the forest, your eye catches an inconspicuous cave. Without hesitation, you rush straight into the very depth of it...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/d5aa27ec0d6abc440032790d1c179f18.poster.avif?t=1773782579\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/d5aa27ec0d6abc440032790d1c179f18.webm?t=1773782579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/d5aa27ec0d6abc440032790d1c179f18.mp4?t=1773782579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Procedural generation of levels. With procedurally generated levels, no two runs are ever the same, allowing for countless hours of gameplay.<br></li><li>Decide on how you want to play. Choose a unique class, race, and then continue to customize your character's appearance.<br></li><li>Play by exploring and combining any skill tree of your choice.<br></li><li>Challenge a unique setup of random curses that weaken your character. Find magic books containing powerful enchantments that help dispel the darkness.<br></li><li>Explore unique areas, each holds a variety of dangers, such as creepy monsters, exclusive bosses, and unrivaled traps.<br></li><li>Collect a full set of armor or combine different types. Create the strongest character ever.<br></li><li>Find all the secret levels to explore extensive locations with cities never seen before.<br></li><li>Non-target action combat</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/4d296e24b004850589d137c98c18c181.poster.avif?t=1773782579\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/4d296e24b004850589d137c98c18c181.webm?t=1773782579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2629410/extras/4d296e24b004850589d137c98c18c181.mp4?t=1773782579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
